'''动作冒险游戏'''（{{lang-en|Action-adventure game}}，簡稱A-AVG）:是[[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]的分支，它融合了[[动作游戏|动作游戏]]的一些特征。<ref name=Puzzle1>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/2917/designing_and_integrating_puzzles_.php?page=1|title=Designing and Integrating Puzzles in Action-Adventure Games|last=Luban|first=Pascal|page=1|work=Gamasutra|publisher=Think Services Game Group|date=2002-12-06|access-date=2009-02-05| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081221140043/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/2917/designing_and_integrating_puzzles_.php?page=1| archive-date= 21 December 2008 }}</ref>游戏过程中玩家除了需要探索找到游戏过关的关键物品，通过各种各样的险要的地形之外，还可能需要与游戏中的其他角色进行战斗。<ref>{{cite book|last=Rollings|first=Andrew|author2=Ernest Adams|title=Fundamentals of Game Design|publisher=Prentice Hall|year=2006|url=http://wps.prenhall.com/bp_gamedev_1/54/14053/3597646.cw/index.html|isbn=0-13-168747-6|access-date=2021-07-05|archive-date=2017-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231072651/http://wps.prenhall.com/bp_gamedev_1/54/14053/3597646.cw/index.html}}</ref>

